channel.title: Live: Wimbledon 2025
channel.desc: Live tennis continues from the All England Club, where the first of the men's and ladies' quarter-finals in the singles being played. On this day in 2024, Jasmine Paolini ruthlessly dispatched American Emma Navarro, winning 6-2, 6-1. The diminutive Italian eventually progressed to the final before losing to Czech Barbora Krejcikova.
